## Section A: Verification Plan — Aviation Extensions

### Additional Fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `dal` | Enum | `DAL A` / `DAL B` / `DAL C` / `DAL D` / `DAL E` — highest DAL of any requirement covered by this plan |
| `applicable_standard` | List | Applicable standards (e.g. `DO-178C`, `DO-254`, `DO-160G`, `ARP4754A`) |
| `verification_objective_ref` | String | Reference to the specific standard objective being satisfied by this plan |
| `independence_required` | Boolean | Whether independent verification is required — derived from `dal` per SK-VV-001-AVN Section A |
| `independent_reviewer` | Reference | Designated independent reviewer — required when `independence_required = true` |
| `soi_stage` | Enum | `SOI #1` / `SOI #2` / `SOI #3` / `SOI #4` — Stage of Involvement milestone this plan supports |
| `certification_basis_ref` | Text | Applicable airworthiness regulations this plan addresses (e.g. FAR 25.1309, CS-25) |
| `moc_ref` | String | Means of Compliance reference (MOC 1–MOC 10 per AC 20-115 / AC 20-152) |
| `psac_ref` | String | Reference to the Plan for Software Aspects of Certification (DO-178C programs) |
| `phac_ref` | String | Reference to the Plan for Hardware Aspects of Certification (DO-254 programs) |

### Recommendations
- `dal` propagates from the Verification Plan to all child Test Cases and Verification Results — surface it prominently in the graph model.
- `independence_required` must be derived automatically from `dal` per the DAL-specific rules in SK-VV-001-AVN Section A, not set manually. Manual override requires documented rationale.
- `soi_stage` supports DER/ACO coordination milestones. Update this field as the program progresses through each SOI review to maintain audit readiness.

