## Section F: DAL-Driven Rule Summary

| DAL | Independence Required | Structural Coverage | Anomaly Report on Fail | Witness Typical |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| DAL A | Yes — full independence, second signature on result | MC/DC | Yes — required field | Yes |
| DAL B | Yes — independent review of requirements, design, test cases | Decision | Yes — required field | Sometimes |
| DAL C | Independence for software verification review | Statement | Yes — recommended | Rarely |
| DAL D | No formal requirement; peer review expected | N/A | Recommended | No |
| DAL E | No requirement | N/A | No | No |

**Note:** The independence rules above summarize SK-VV-001-AVN Section A for reference. SK-VV-001-AVN is the authoritative source — this table must not be used in place of it.

